bci.<\/li>\n<li><b>\u015aled\u017a zmiany w polityce Amazon.<\/b> B\u0105d\u017a na bie\u017c\u0105co z regulacjami, kt\u00f3re mog\u0105 wp\u0142ywa\u0107 na Twoj\u0105 mark\u0119, szczeg\u00f3lnie w bran\u017cy kosmetycznej i FMCG.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Podsumowuj\u0105c, utrzymanie rejestracji marki na Amazonie jest kluczowe dla sukcesu Twojego biznesu. B\u0105d\u017a czujny i podejmuj dzia\u0142ania, aby chroni\u0107 swoj\u0105 mark\u0119 przed nieprzewidzianymi trudno\u015bciami. <\/p>\n<p><b>Masz wi\u0119cej pyta\u0144? Skontaktuj si\u0119 z nami.<\/b><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<h1>Jak chroni\u0107 swoj\u0105 mark\u0119 na Amazonie: Kluczowe wskaz\u00f3wki dla sprzedawc\u00f3w<\/h1>\n<p>Czy kiedykolwiek z<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":6464,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[5],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-6463","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-strategia"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/6463"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=6463"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/6463\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/6464"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=6463"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=6463"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"ht